<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wạnạ ʿlyl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (wạnạ ʿlyl fy lyl ṭwyl .. wʿdk dlyl rạḥ yhdyny
 wạlqạk bnwr btsẖq swr .. ḥzny ạlly kạn bybkyny)2
 wạrtwy bgẖnạk wạrtmy fy ḥmạk .. lmạ ạftkr ḍʿfy bmrạr
 (wạlqạny fyk nqsẖ f ạ̹ydyk .. ạ̉sẖbʿ ạ̉mạn fy wsṭ nạr)2
 fy wsṭ nạr
 2- (wf qlb ạlkẖwf gẖyrk mạ ạsẖwf .. ạ̉jy ạrtmy bḥmly ʿlyk
 wạnsy̱ ạlbkạ lmạ ạlsẖfạ .. ybqy̱ skyb mạ byn ạ̹ydyk)2
 wạʿysẖ wyạk sẖbʿạn blqạk .. ạsmk byjry fy ạlʿrwq
 (tsẖfy wtrfʿ tsby wtjʿl .. ạ̉nhạr myạh byn ạlsẖqwq)2
 byn ạlsẖqwq</lyrics>
<author>hạny ạ̉nys, mnạl smyr fryd</author>
